{"tid":2333383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"待檢疫女子家中離世　陳肇始：衞生署已做了很多工作","createTime":"2020-12-20T10:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T10:55:35.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca24d2e7d1144a92e3a32b035756419996bdb6f","tid":2333383,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"大圍美林邨一名62歲女子日前在家中單獨等候送往檢疫中心期間離世，死者女兒批評是政府行政失當，導致媽媽死亡。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始到黃大仙彩雲邨視察流動採樣站，被問到政府有否行政失當、會否就事件道歉，陳肇始說，衞生署已經做了很多工作。被問到會否有其他改善工作，她無再回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好勤力但係唔合格"}]}